import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['speed'], bins=50, color='blue', alpha=0.5)
    plt.axvline(data['speed'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean')
    plt.axvline(data['speed'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind speed?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['dir'].plot(kind='hist', bins=36, color='blue', edgecolor='black')
    plt.axvline(data['dir'].median(), color='red', label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['dir'].median()))
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind directions?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.scatter(data['dir'], data['speed'])
    ax.set_xlabel('Direction')
    ax.set_ylabel('Speed')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between wind speed and direction?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['dirCat'] = data['dirCat'].astype(str)
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.boxplot(data.groupby('dirCat')['speed'].apply(list), labels=data['dirCat'].unique())
    ax.set_xlabel('Wind Direction')
    ax.set_ylabel('Wind Speed')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind speeds in different directions?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 10))
    heatmap = ax.scatter(data['longitude'], data['latitude'], c=data['speed'], cmap='coolwarm', alpha=0.8)
    plt.colorbar(heatmap, ax=ax)
    ax.set_xlabel('Longitude')
    ax.set_ylabel('Latitude')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind speeds at different locations?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
